{"type":"message","id":"5c925aa5","parentId":"6182c400","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:40:59.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself that just ran. This is the cron job's own session. There are no other user conversations in the last 5 minutes. So I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for the latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"5f78ab1b98ce31e0bb93fd7fb6f39d827f8f05bf2496d1c92ba41f80e498b063"},{"type":"text","text":"没有活跃对话（仅检测到cron自身的会话），执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ad6tcfp4cp35_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main:","limit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":810,"output":122,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44913,"cost":{"input":0.000243,"output":0.00014639999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00170883}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774698054251}}
