{"type":"message","id":"9a1b1f72","parentId":"5d99737d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:41:01.589Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The main session has no messages. Now let me search for the latest industry trends.","thinkingSignature":"98f8b5c6cb482f9a2bfbcfaeb81b8be442fbba479aa9c7937532e5b275b17a3a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rcfvfneq3ulw_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1001,"output":61,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45043,"cost":{"input":0.0003003,"output":0.00007319999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0016929299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774698059368}}
{"type":"message","id":"62ab5f0e","parentId":"9a1b1f72","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:41:01.595Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rcfvfneq3ulw_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774698061592}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f9a7ecb","parentId":"62ab5f0e","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:41:04.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I know how to use web search. Let me search for industry trends related to 道简网络's business areas.","thinkingSignature":"67c37f406893165afaa22ac24c868137283bdbc6e5f08758136ed0a70c03cc26"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_v62n352h71ug_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策趋势\" --output json 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1577,"output":86,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45644,"cost":{"input":0.00047309999999999995,"output":0.0001032,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00189573}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774698061595}}
