{"type":"message","id":"1678a80c","parentId":"1770d98d","timestamp":"2026-03-28T11:42:46.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've completed the autonomous learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"43ea0b40b73441531089c3504b81e4a525c3ef7a98144cf571b2d0afc4c3ae51"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已完成空闲检测自主学习，无活跃对话 → 执行了行业动态研究并保存。\n\n**本次学习内容（2026-03-28 19:40）：**\n\n1. **企业数字化转型政策趋势** - \"十五五\"规划、数据要素政策、中小企业30%补贴、AI+工业互联网融合\n2. **智能安防行业趋势** - AI大模型重构生态、边缘智能+5G-A、万亿市场规模、隐私合规成核心议题\n3. **网络系统集成与IT运维趋势** - AIOps驱动主动防御、AI原生网络、运维外包持续增长\n\n已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`，包含5条关键启示，涵盖道简网络三大业务线的最新行业动态分析。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":5484,"output":185,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49650,"cost":{"input":0.0016451999999999999,"output":0.000222,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031866299999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774698160362}}
